ATAC-seq in Bioconductor exercises

Tom Carroll

In todays session we will work with some of the ATAC-seq data of T-regulatory cells from Christina Leslies lab.

Aligned data as a BAM file can be found here.

The peak calls for ATAC-seq data can be found here

ATAC-seq analysis.
